HEADWORD: Anthropomorphize
<hw>An`thro*po*mor"phize</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos>
<def>To attribute a human form or personality to.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>You may see imaginative children every day
<qex>anthropomorphizing</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Lowell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Anthropomorphology</ent>⟦br⟧
